## RBAC (система прав)

- Enterprise DB-backed RBAC, `rbac_*` таблицы в PostgreSQL
- 5 системных ролей: `admin`, `manager`, `employee`, `photographer`, `client`
- 21 permission
- Backend: `authenticateToken` + `requirePermission('perm:slug')`
- Frontend: `permissionsSignal` из `GET /api/auth/me`
- `requireRole()` — DEPRECATED, использовать `requirePermission()`

### Матрица прав

| Permission | admin | manager | employee | photographer |
|------------|:-----:|:-------:|:--------:|:------------:|
| `inbox:view` | + | + | + | + |
| `inbox:manage` | + | + | + | — |
| `chat:reply` | + | + | + | + |
| `chat:assign` | + | + | + | — |
| `tasks:manage` | + | + | + | + |
| `pos:use` | + | + | + | — |
| `team:chat` | + | + | + | + |
| `bookings:manage` | + | + | + | + |
| `production:manage` | + | + | + | — |
| `pricing:read` | + | + | + | — |
| `pricing:manage` | + | + | — | — |
| `clients:view` | + | + | — | + |
| `catalog:manage` | + | + | — | — |
| `subscriptions:manage` | + | + | — | — |
| `analytics:view` | + | + | — | — |
| `shifts:manage` | + | + | — | — |
| `reports:view` | + | + | — | — |
| `workflows:manage` | + | + | — | — |
| `partners:manage` | + | + | — | — |
| `users:manage` | + | — | — | — |
| `settings:manage` | + | — | — | — |

