|------|-----------|
| `src/app/app.routes.ts` | Все маршруты (CRM = lazy route) |
| `src/app/core/services/auth.service.ts` | JWT auth + permissionsSignal |
| `src/app/core/services/visitor-chat.service.ts` | WebSocket чат |
