| `backend/src/services/outbound-queue.service.ts` | BullMQ outbound queues |
| `backend/src/services/connectors/inbound-pipeline.ts` | Unified inbound |
| `backend/src/middleware/auth.ts` | authenticateToken + requirePermission |
| `backend/src/middleware/errorHandler.ts` | AppError class |
| `ecosystem.config.cjs` | PM2 config |

