## Singleton-механизм (Active-Passive)

- Node.js schedulers: `pg_try_advisory_lock(737001)` — лидер, follower retry 30s
- Systemd timers: `/usr/local/bin/run-once.sh` с PG advisory lock
- BullMQ workers: на leader-ноде (concurrency=5 per channel)

---

## Интеграции

- Claude — AI чат-бот
- CloudPayments — приём платежей
- Telegram Bot API (grammy) — webhook mode
- VK Callback API — webhook mode
- Max Bot API — webhook mode
- WhatsApp Cloud API — webhook + HMAC
- Instagram Graph API — webhook + HMAC + 24h reply window
- Managed Redis — кэш, Socket.IO adapter, BullMQ

- Angular Service Worker (ngsw) — PWA + push

